## 📁 Project Overview

This is a full-stack marketing agency website with:
- **Frontend**: Modern, animated HTML/CSS/JavaScript website
- **Backend**: Node.js/Express REST API with MongoDB
- **Features**: Contact forms, portfolio management, newsletter, admin panel, file uploads, email notifications

